body:
The data files for PhysicsTools/PatUtils are also part of cms-data/PhysicsTools-PatUtils reposiotry. These deleted files are identical as the one available in https://github.com/cms-data/PhysicsTools-PatUtils. 

Once merged we need a full IB to avoid picking up data files from CMSSW/poison directory
title: cleanup PhysicsTools/PatUtils data files
